{"tid":2504974,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【理大衝突】趙柱幫：警擬上門拘兩涉事者 惟當事人已流亡或搬離單位","createTime":"2021-04-26T09:19:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-26T10:21:29.000Z","uid":283837,"like":25,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"5433565d4a032d1c316309615a543bb2714f0554","tid":2504974,"uid":283837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T09:19:44.000Z","msg":"理工大學在2019年11月發生衝突，警方包圍理大校園，並與示威者對峙。警方隨後以非法集結等罪拘捕多人。沙田區議員趙柱幫表示，再有涉及理大事件的人士被警方上門拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n趙柱幫今早在社交媒體發文指，一名現已流亡，但曾在理大衝突期間進入理大的女義務急救員，收到其位於香港的家人通知，有警員於今日早上5時上門拘捕。另有一名同涉及理大事件的人士亦指，今早亦接獲家人通知有警員上門，但該名人士已搬離原本居住的單位。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/1556776/即時-港聞-理大衝突-趙柱幫-警擬上門拘兩涉事者-惟當事人已流亡或搬離單位\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F1556776%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-%E8%B6%99%E6%9F%B1%E5%B9%AB-%E8%AD%A6%E6%93%AC%E4%B8%8A%E9%96%80%E6%8B%98%E5%85%A9%E6%B6%89%E4%BA%8B%E8%80%85-%E6%83%9F%E7%95%B6%E4%BA%8B%E4%BA%BA%E5%B7%B2%E6%B5%81%E4%BA%A1%E6%88%96%E6%90%AC%E9%9B%A2%E5%96%AE%E4%BD%8D&d=D9q%2FqAhMrjKrs4nvjauepEzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=aa0aa19a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F1556776%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-%E8%B6%99%E6%9F%B1%E5%B9%AB-%E8%AD%A6%E6%93%AC%E4%B8%8A%E9%96%80%E6%8B%98%E5%85%A9%E6%B6%89%E4%BA%8B%E8%80%85-%E6%83%9F%E7%95%B6%E4%BA%8B%E4%BA%BA%E5%B7%B2%E6%B5%81%E4%BA%A1%E6%88%96%E6%90%AC%E9%9B%A2%E5%96%AE%E4%BD%8D&h=cef47f48\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/1556776/即時-港聞-理大衝突-趙柱幫-警擬上門拘兩涉事者-惟當事人已流亡或搬離單位</a>"},{"pid":"8cfed4836d37e4fe59058ca4039bdd9b6e3fff6f","tid":2504974,"uid":45785,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T09:21:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/-2017-11-27-9.11.52_844035867